{"tid":273274,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"滙控發10億坡元永久或有可換股證券","createTime":"2017-06-06T12:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T14:42:31.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b91986767ed01653ffdc1816536cb32cd0e6a830","tid":273274,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170606/large/1496749680_7872.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170606%2Flarge%2F1496749680_7872.jpg&h=e57ca818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滙控（005）公布，發行總值10億元新加坡元的永久後償或有可轉換證券，初步年息率訂為4.7厘，以中間市場掉期利率加287點子水平作參考，有關證券可於發行5年後起（2022年），每5年可重設1次日期；發行人擬申請將是批證券在愛爾蘭證券交易所上市。<br />\n<br />\n根據巴三規定，倘滙控普通股權一級資本比率（CET1）任何時候低於7%，或因應英國審慎監管局要求，便會構成觸發資本充足規定要求，有關證券將按轉換價，轉換為滙控普通股，以充實集團核心資本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56792530&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56792530%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170606&d=rLrftLDsJd6NcaqFflm%2FegHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=3abfb026\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56792530%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170606&h=c8c28aec\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56792530&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170606</a>"},{"pid":"a678dfb6807751fc5e61b21fb18567f89476fa79","tid":273274,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:14:09.000Z","msg":"點解唔用USD ?"},{"pid":"c16dcc2c18cd8487d685b55202d28b9450080624","tid":273274,"uid":35331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"Coco<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji